column17:
Product Description

His husky baritone invokes memories of a memorable night and the authority that he radiates sends people scurrying to do his bidding. Assuming power comes easily to him for he a born leader. He demands only the best not only from people around him but also from his own self pushing hard and further into the boundaries of possibility to achieve what no man has achieved yet. His slow yet steady climb into the creme de la creme of society and power is not without its scars ones that are well-hidden by the overwhelming presence of Number One from the celebrated house of Boss. The luxury Eau de Toilette is like a seductive companion who wraps her silken fingers over his heart and soul and keeps him enslaved to its wrenching aroma. Accords of artemisia green apple juniper basil grapefruit caraway bergamot and lemon create a luminous opening which bursts his day wide open in a flurry of freshness. Notes in the heart blend accords of honey lavender orris root jasmine sage with the floral tones of lily of the valley rose and geranium which instigates action and strength within him during a packed day. The dry down departs and leaves behind a trail with the accords of sandalwood amber patchouli musk oakmoss cedar and tobacco with just a hint of spicy cinnamon. The allure of Hugo Boss Number One is presented to world in a simple flacon through which the clear amber of the fragrance peeks out proving yet again that the most potent things come in the most innocuous of packages. Feel yourself go heady as the sweeping notes of Boss Number One takes over your senses.

For the man whose dreams run in tune with the melody of violins and saxophones this luxury scent strikes the right chord. Revelling in his own rhythm Yves Saint Laurent Live Jazz appeals to the suave yet unconventional gentleman. Created by Pierre Bourdon this sensuous Eau De Toilette is made for the iconic house of Yves Saint Laurent. The top note weaves together zesty notes of lemon the uplifting scent of grapefruit and cooling hints of mint reminiscent of a refreshing mojito on a balmy afternoon. Emerging shortly after this is the heart note that treats you to the herbaceous spice of coriander against the delicious sweet-sour nuance of rhubarb. Finally the base note transports you to your favourite club downtown with the warm and woody scent of cedar along with sharp spicy nutmeg resinous amber and hints of rich vanilla. Delve into the music just as this enriching aroma envelops you in a laidback yet vibrant aura. You can wear this scent at any time and let its smooth and invigorating appeal instantly lift your spirits. Topped with a subtle black atomiser the clear and elegant structure exudes an air of tranquility. So grab your axe and get in the groove because tonight is all about the blues.

Deadly and luscious this luxury scent takes you on an unparalleled journey filled with mystique and intrigue. With just a delicate spritz of Yves Saint Laurent Opium for every step you take - demand a second glance and a loyal admirers heart. Exquisitely crafted this Eau De Toilette is a jewel in the crown of the legendary house of Yves Saint Laurent. Start your olfactory journey from the top note that mixes refreshing mandarin sweet notes of bergamot and clean green hints of lily of the valley. Travelling into the heart you are met with a delectable combination of exotic jasmine vivacious notes of carnation balanced with bitter and aromatic myrrh. The fragrance dries down with a heavenly base note of creamy rich vanilla earthy patchouli smoky notes of amber and pleasing hints of sweet myrrh. A sensual fragrance that holds you within its surreal trance it is perfect to complete your evening ensemble for that special night out. The chinoiserie inspired vial radiates a decadent appeal indulging the epicurean senses that lie deep within you. Bathed in contrasting shades of glowing vesper and molten gold this square-shaped vial is simple yet grandiose and commands attention. If your bewitching eyes arresting smile and graceful demeanour weren't enough to hold them captive unleash your secret weapon - your Opium.

Product Description

Wake up to the smell of espresso and baguettes wafting from the nearby cafe visit the iconic Moulin Rouge followed by a stroll down Champs-Élysées and who wouldn't fall in love with Paris. Yves Saint Laurent pays the ultimate tribute to the city he adores with an enigmatic Eau de Parfum. A luxury scent created by perfumer Sophia Grojsman Yves Saint Laurent Paris is for the woman who embodies the spirit of this city-chic elegant and cutting edge. Opening with a top note of soft and hazy mimose extracts beautiful notes of orange blossom and the unmistakably feminine hint of rose along with spicy and intense cassia sweet hints of bergamot and nasturcia pleasant hawthorn light floral hyacinth and powdery lemon geranium. Flowing into the heart of the scent you can take in a fragrant combination of light hints of violet fresh lily exotic jasmine slightly bitter orris root bright and refreshing lime blossom mesmerising ylang-ylang and clean green hints of lily of the valley. Finishing off this fragrance is the enticing base note of sweet green iris rich sandalwood smoky amber soothing mush along with organic hints of oakmoss warming cedar and heliotrope that is reminiscent of almonds. Wear this fragrance as you would adorn yourself with your favourite dress for that occasion that deserves nothing less than perfection. The crowning glory to your immaculate ensemble this perfume whisks you away to the most romantic city on earth with just a whiff.
